# This directory is populated at build time by scripts/fetch-portable-python.{ps1,sh}
# with a python-build-standalone interpreter, which is bundled into the installer so
# end users do NOT need to install Python themselves ("portable Python").
#
# The interpreter is intentionally NOT committed (tens of MB). Run the fetch script
# before `tauri build` (CI does this automatically). If this folder contains only
# this .gitkeep at build time, the app gracefully falls back to system Python.
